The vulnerability-class taxonomy in the `web-app-testing` methodology skill is informed by the
`skills/vulnerabilities/` library in Strix (https://github.com/usestrix/strix).

This skill was authored clean-room: only the methodology structure (which vulnerability classes to
test, WSTG alignment) was adapted; no source text or code was copied. Attribution is provided as a
courtesy and to record provenance.

